            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"9665XXXXXXXX\",\n  \"password\": \"YourPassword@1\"\n}"
            },
            "url": "{{baseUrl}}user/auth/login",
            "description": "**Endpoint:** `user/auth/login` (`ApiConstants.login`)\n\n**Body (مقترح — يطابق شاشة Login):**\n| Key | Type | ملاحظة |\n|-----|------|--------|\n| phone | string | أرقام إنجليزية بعد `toEnglishNumbers()` |\n| password | string | نفس قواعد `Validators.validatePassword` |\n\n**Response — `data` (مقترح):** انظر Example \"200 success\".\n"
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 success — token + user",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [],
                "body": {
                  "mode": "raw",
                  "raw": "{\n  \"phone\": \"966512345678\",\n  \"password\": \"Secret@1a\"\n}"
                },
                "url": "{{baseUrl}}user/auth/login"
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
